			<outline text="August 23" type="calendarDay" name="23" >
				<outline text="My professor has to teach his class in person today. At a university where they are not requiring anyone to actually be vaccinated.  Tomorrow the small child that lives with me goes back to school in person.

Here we go.  #savemylife" type="tweet" created="Mon, 23 Aug 2021 21:38:12 GMT" tweetId="1429920936262701057" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1429920936262701057" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="Just posted a photo @ Downtown Salt Lake City &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/accounts/login/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 23 Aug 2021 20:19:17 GMT" tweetId="1429901076791283713" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1429901076791283713" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="August 12" type="calendarDay" name="12" >
				<outline text="The right way to approach this is as if it were a new virus and question all your assumptions. 

#DeltaVariant #maskup #savemylife" type="tweet" created="Thu, 12 Aug 2021 17:41:18 GMT" tweetId="1425875053925732359" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1425875053925732359" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
