			<outline text="August 8" type="calendarDay" name="08" >
				<outline text="one two. one two. one two. it's my job to keep my hooman very safe on that bike of hers that goes nowhere. #dogsoftwitter #peloton &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1424514158783959043/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 08 Aug 2021 23:33:36 GMT" tweetId="1424514158783959043" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1424514158783959043" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="This does not surprise me, but I'm still playing my own sad trombone. It's the right thing to do, I'm just really tired of putting my #joy on hold.  Part of me just wants to start swimming for #newzealand. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/jazzfest/status/1424445674511290369&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 08 Aug 2021 20:03:12 GMT" tweetId="1424461211517652995" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1424461211517652995" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="August 3" type="calendarDay" name="03" >
				<outline text="And #backtoschool we go. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/BenWinslow/status/1422579083762823171&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 03 Aug 2021 17:57:53 GMT" tweetId="1422617732650991617" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1422617732650991617" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="August 2" type="calendarDay" name="02" >
				<outline text="They are marching for their lives. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/leedam18102/status/1422189724739936257&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 14:21:43 GMT" tweetId="1422200947489402885" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1422200947489402885" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="Let’s not forget them. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/springrv22222/status/1422192886452428808&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 14:20:04 GMT" tweetId="1422200531192217606" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1422200531192217606" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
