		<outline text="July 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="july2021" >
			<outline text="July 31" type="calendarDay" name="31" >
				<outline text="Standing in my kitchen having a midlife Sam Fox moment and then thought, “I wonder how they are all holding up in the #pandemic?” For reals. They all live in my ❤️. #betterthings &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1421663864429547520/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 01 Aug 2021 02:47:33 GMT" tweetId="1421663864429547520" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1421663864429547520" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="Updating our mask policy today at the clinic. 

#freebritney @ Downtown Salt Lake City &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/accounts/login/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 31 Jul 2021 19:16:51 GMT" tweetId="1421550444640415745" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1421550444640415745" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 28" type="calendarDay" name="28" >
				<outline text="RUSS WALKER, owner of MERIDIAN HEIGHTS, might want to rethink management of his SENIOR APARTMENTS in #Sandy, #Utah. He hides behind them and refuses to take RESPONSIBILITY.  Meanwhile, tenants are suffering! No AC, No Running Water. @KSL @KLSMatt" type="tweet" created="Wed, 28 Jul 2021 20:55:19 GMT" tweetId="1420488061658419200" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1420488061658419200" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="MERIDIAN HEIGHTS APARTMENTS in #SANDY #Utah has total disregard for its elderly residents. NO AC for days. No running water. EXORBITANT RENT. @KSLmatt this is a STORY FOR YOU! I promise this is just one example of many in the #SLC valley." type="tweet" created="Wed, 28 Jul 2021 20:17:18 GMT" tweetId="1420478492261584897" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1420478492261584897" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 27" type="calendarDay" name="27" >
				<outline text="My heart 💜 walking around on four furry paws. 

I am so thankful he chose me. 

#dogmomlife @ 9th and 9th &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/accounts/login/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 27 Jul 2021 15:14:48 GMT" tweetId="1420039976587247617" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1420039976587247617" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 26" type="calendarDay" name="26" >
				<outline text="Whatever you do today, do it with the confidence of this kid sporting his supercalifragilistic rainbow 🌈 cape! 

There is nothing you can not do. 💜 @ Harvey Milk Blvd &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/accounts/login/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 13:35:07 GMT" tweetId="1419652505202577413" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1419652505202577413" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 25" type="calendarDay" name="25" >
				<outline text="There are 7 billion stories playing out each and every day on this planet.  I am trying my very best never to be the villain in a single one of them. ✌🏻" type="tweet" created="Sun, 25 Jul 2021 22:42:26 GMT" tweetId="1419427852122955776" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1419427852122955776" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 21" type="calendarDay" name="21" >
				<outline text="It has been a DAY!!! 

However no day is a bad day that ends with paddle boarding and swimming with your sister. 

#goodgoodday @ Bear Lake North Beach &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CRnIUqCBSf4/?utm_medium=twitter&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 01:42:20 GMT" tweetId="1418023574791729154" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1418023574791729154" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 15" type="calendarDay" name="15" >
				<outline text="It's always been more than a bike. #onepeloton  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nakedjen.com/nakedjen/2021/07/how-it-startedhow-it-is-going-.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 18:45:05 GMT" tweetId="1415744245160235008" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1415744245160235008" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 14" type="calendarDay" name="14" >
				<outline text="Just posted a photo @ The Salty Sanctuary &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CRVN5V9hxbw/?utm_medium=twitter&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 02:44:44 GMT" tweetId="1415502561314938882" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1415502561314938882" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 13" type="calendarDay" name="13" >
				<outline text="Hi Frens. I am Clyde. Famous for #vegan cookies. And for my devotion to my mom. #dogs #dogsoftwitter #tongueouttuesday &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1415026737763684353/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 19:13:58 GMT" tweetId="1415026737763684353" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1415026737763684353" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="Every single one of these women #savedmylife during the #pandemic with their exquisite acting abilities. They all have already won and I'm glad I do not have to vote. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TelevisionAcad/status/1414972998130434049&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 17:39:24 GMT" tweetId="1415002938011832321" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1415002938011832321" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 11" type="calendarDay" name="11" >
				<outline text="Denny's serves #vegan bacon.  Denny's.  Some day I will share my story of a 3 am stop at Denny's where I ended up rescuing a dog (that I later reunited with his owner), but for now...DENNY'S SERVES #VEGAN BACON!" type="tweet" created="Sun, 11 Jul 2021 22:05:27 GMT" tweetId="1414345115250794496" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1414345115250794496" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 9" type="calendarDay" name="09" >
				<outline text="Just posted a photo @ Oregon Country Fair &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CRHPznuh8BC/?utm_medium=twitter&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 16:32:03 GMT" tweetId="1413536436050092036" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1413536436050092036" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 4" type="calendarDay" name="04" >
				<outline text="Just posted a photo @ The Salty Sanctuary &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CQ6e3PUB3cY/?utm_medium=twitter&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 04 Jul 2021 17:33:29 GMT" tweetId="1411739956649811975" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1411739956649811975" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 1" type="calendarDay" name="01" >
				<outline text="If you actually live in #Utah, you may want to read this entire thread. And consider still #masking even if you ARE #vaccinated. #Delta is highly contagious and our hospitals are FULL. #savemylife &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/RobertGehrke/status/1410650031787429888&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 01 Jul 2021 18:11:07 GMT" tweetId="1410662267021004801" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1410662267021004801" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="I am so sad I missed this golden ticket opportunity.  These would have made some very beautiful #ART. xo &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/PatinkinMandy/status/1410394837132660736&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 01 Jul 2021 18:01:13 GMT" tweetId="1410659771691114502" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1410659771691114502" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			</outline>
		<outline text="June 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="june2021" >
			<outline text="June 29" type="calendarDay" name="29" >
				<outline text="The problem is that has NOT been my experience so far.  I was prepared for hiccups, but like you, I do not like all the ADS in #podcasts.  So if I am paying the piper, I want what they say the will deliver. I liked your suggestion! #paycasts" type="tweet" created="Tue, 29 Jun 2021 18:26:12 GMT" tweetId="1409941285260062720" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409941285260062720" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="@davewiner re PAYCASTS.  This is what @apple told me about their podcasts subscription service: &quot;Listeners can hear new and original shows, and get early access to new seasons of critically acclaimed and fan-favorite series, all ad-free!&quot;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 29 Jun 2021 18:24:44 GMT" tweetId="1409940917516083203" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409940917516083203" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 28" type="calendarDay" name="28" >
				<outline text="#VenmoMe @Jennifer-Neal-20 https://t.co/h7aRAHeRF7" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 18:11:21 GMT" tweetId="1409575159866920961" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409575159866920961" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 27" type="calendarDay" name="27" >
				<outline text=".@onepeloton when are the VR headsets coming?  During my run this morning, I also thought: Imagine being on the bike, but *riding* this route with @jesskingnyc and sharing all the #joy and PRIDE. xo" type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 21:22:48 GMT" tweetId="1409260953141530626" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409260953141530626" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="This morning I did a *run* with @jesskingnyc in my ears and my heart along the entire Pride Parade route in #NYC. It was pure magic. We should be proud to show up exactly as we are https://t.co/3WiOT3SoeF. #loveislove https://t.co/6eaEdH99Pl" type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 21:06:25 GMT" tweetId="1409256828886601731" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409256828886601731" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 26" type="calendarDay" name="26" >
				<outline text="All those years I have showed up at weddings #naked.  I've been doing it wrong! #truestory https://t.co/AXviF5p6SM" type="tweet" created="Sat, 26 Jun 2021 18:51:21 GMT" tweetId="1408860450394017800" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1408860450394017800" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 23" type="calendarDay" name="23" >
				<outline text="I signed up for the SCHRUTE FARMS BED &amp;amp; BREAKFAST 5K/10K!  It's like these people have actually met me or something??  

 https://t.co/7CC54h0DEh https://t.co/7CC54h0DEh" type="tweet" created="Wed, 23 Jun 2021 21:22:58 GMT" tweetId="1407811440904261632" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1407811440904261632" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="I have a #NYC phone number.  I received over 30 calls/texts yesterday reminding me to #vote. 

That's a lot of robots." type="tweet" created="Wed, 23 Jun 2021 15:57:03 GMT" tweetId="1407729422304641037" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1407729422304641037" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 22" type="calendarDay" name="22" >
				<outline text="This is perhaps one the BEST things our mayor has done all year. Thank you.  It won't STOP IT because #FREEDOM, but it may help reduce the insanity. https://t.co/LFOyb132or" type="tweet" created="Tue, 22 Jun 2021 21:22:06 GMT" tweetId="1407448838068006916" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1407448838068006916" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
