https://t.co/wFX3xNXiYf" type="tweet" created="Sun, 20 Jun 2021 19:32:57 GMT" tweetId="1406696592485220356" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1406696592485220356" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
